2. 问题: 对比各门店的租赁履约效率：计算每家门店已归还租赁的平均租期（天）和归还率（归还数/总租赁数），仅含至少10条租赁记录的门店
   原始错误: 函数 round(interval, integer) 不存在
LINE 1: EXPLAIN SELECT i.store_id AS 门店ID, ROUND(AVG(r.return_date...
                                             ^
HINT:  没有匹配指定名称和参数类型的函数. 您也许需要增加明确的类型转换.
   修复后SQL:
   SELECT i.store_id AS 门店ID, ROUND(AVG(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM (r.return_date - r.rental_date)) / 86400), 1) AS 平均租期_天, ROUND(COUNT(r.return_date) * 100.0 / COUNT(*), 2) AS 归还率_百分比 FROM public.rental r JOIN public.inventory i ON r.inventory_id = i.inventory_id GROUP BY i.store_id HAVING COUNT(*) >= 10 ORDER BY 归还率_百分比 DESC;
----------------------------------------

3. 问题: 查询过去一年中租赁频次突增的客户：对比2004年与2005年各客户的年度租赁次数，筛选出2005年租赁数比2004年增长超过100%的客户，显示客户ID、2004年次数、2005年次数、增长率
   原始错误: trailing junk after numeric literal 在 "2004年租赁次数" 或附近的
LINE 1: ....customer_id AS 客户ID, COALESCE(y2004.cnt, 0) AS 2004年租赁...
                                                             ^
   修复后SQL:
   WITH yearly_counts AS (SELECT r.customer_id, EXTRACT(YEAR FROM r.rental_date) AS year, COUNT(*) AS cnt FROM public.rental r WHERE EXTRACT(YEAR FROM r.rental_date) IN (2004, 2005) GROUP BY r.customer_id, year) SELECT y2004.customer_id AS "客户ID", COALESCE(y2004.cnt, 0) AS "2004年租赁次数", COALESCE(y2005.cnt, 0) AS "2005年租赁次数", ROUND((COALESCE(y2005.cnt, 0) - COALESCE(y2004.cnt, 0)) * 100.0 / NULLIF(COALESCE(y2004.cnt, 0), 0), 2) AS "增长率_百分比" FROM (SELECT customer_id, cnt FROM yearly_counts WHERE year = 2004) y2004 FULL OUTER JOIN (SELECT customer_id, cnt FROM yearly_counts WHERE year = 2005) y2005 ON y2004.customer_id = y2005.customer_id WHERE COALESCE(y2005.cnt, 0) > COALESCE(y2004.cnt, 0) * 2 AND COALESCE(y2004.cnt, 0) > 0;
